---------
 EC Test
=========

EC test source and include files to test errors on it's self.

To test change to 'test' directory first.
cd test

To setup (run both ./cmake.sh and ./makeinstall.sh)
./setup.sh

To cmake on ectest
./cmake

To make and install in bin ectest
./makeinstall.sh

To run tests
./test.sh

To debug with gdb
gdb ./bin/ectest

To check memory leaks with valgrind
valgrind ./bin/ectest


If you change source please renew the test functions related with the changed source.
It's worthy to add new test functions if you add new functionalities.
